    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Capture" kindref="compound">Capture</ref> snapshots the current scene and save as a file. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>@SINCE_1_3.4</para>
<para>Applications should follow the example below to create capture :</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classDali_1_1Capture_1a411b8d93c297db25d0ed94d94d89f534" kindref="member">Capture</ref><sp/>capture<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classDali_1_1Capture_1adce92610e35fcd2eb852af0092ad4cbf" kindref="member">Capture::New</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>If required, you can also connect class member function to a signal :</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">capture.FinishedSignal().Connect(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">this</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>&amp;CaptureSceneExample::OnCaptureFinished);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>At the connected class member function, you can know whether capture finish state.</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>CaptureSceneExample::OnCaptureFinished(<sp/><ref refid="classDali_1_1Capture_1a411b8d93c297db25d0ed94d94d89f534" kindref="member">Capture</ref><sp/>capture,<sp/><ref refid="classDali_1_1Capture_1a65860a46b75abb70ca6cb6371a886093" kindref="member">Capture::FinishState</ref><sp/>state<sp/>)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">if</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(<sp/>state<sp/>==<sp/><ref refid="classDali_1_1Capture_1a65860a46b75abb70ca6cb6371a886093afd9f6519d3f45276829fe74eb2c4bb85" kindref="member">Capture::FinishState::SUCCEEDED</ref><sp/>)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Do<sp/>something</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">else</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Do<sp/>something</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
